---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About Cool Name Maker - Generate Creative Names Online" description="Learn about Cool Name Maker, your go-to platform for generating unique and creative names. Discover our mission, features, and commitment to helping you find the perfect name.">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-40">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">About Cool Name Maker</h1>
        
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                Cool Name Maker was created with a simple yet powerful mission: to help people find perfect, unique, and meaningful names. Whether you're naming a business, character, product, or pet, we provide creative solutions through our advanced name generation technology.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Smart Name Generation</h3>
                    <p>Our intelligent algorithms create unique and contextually relevant names based on your specific requirements and preferences.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">Multiple Categories</h3>
                    <p>From business names to fantasy character names, we cover a wide range of naming needs across different categories.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Why Choose Us</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-4 text-lg">
                <li>Free and easy-to-use platform</li>
                <li>Instant name generation</li>
                <li>Culturally sensitive naming suggestions</li>
                <li>Regular updates and new features</li>
                <li>Community-driven improvements</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Get Started Today</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                Ready to find your perfect name? Start exploring our name generator and discover endless creative possibilities for your naming needs.
            </p>
            <div class="text-center mt-20">
                <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                    Try Name Generator
                </a>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
